Ex-BBNaija ‘Pepper Dem’ housemate, Khafi Kareem Ekpata has explained why she can’t stay angry with her husband, Gedoni Ekpata. The reality star shared a screenshot of the message she got from her husband after she left home for a walk to cool off. The screenshot held a photo of her husband and son looking remorseful accompanied with note that reads: “You can come back home now please we are sorry”. She tagged it with her statement “Why I can’t stay angry at my husband for long lol. I just went for a small walk to get out of the house.”   Actress Stephanie Linus welcomes second child     Firm thrills guests at 2022 AMVCA     Stop shaving your pubic hairs, Blessing CEO advises ladies   Read Also: BBNaija: Met Police issues final warning to Khafi The couple met inside the BBNaija house and began a sizzling relationship which blossomed into a beautiful union. They got engaged in December same year after Khafi said “yes” to Gedoni’s marriage proposal while they vacationed in Cape Verde. The wedding, which was to take place on April 4, 2020 was cancelled due to the social restrictions that trailed the COVID-19 pandemic before they eventually tied the knot in December, 2020 The duo welcomed a son, Miracle Ekpata on August 2021.